humanMachineDialogue.text: According to the pathology report, multiple sentinel lymph nodes and one additional left axillary lymph node were negative for tumor (AJCC pN0). This information aligns with New Rule 11, N0 can indicate that all assessed lymph nodes are negative for metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, the N stage for this patient's cancer is N0.
